rows.label: qst701506_msg0001
rows.name: Hey there! Are you all right?

rows.label: qst701506_msg0004
rows.name:
His breath sounds all wrong.
There might be something blocking
his windpipe.

rows.label: qst701506_msg0005
rows.name:
What should we do? What if he's
having some kind of seizure?

rows.label: qst701506_msg0007
rows.name:
No, it's no use.
You'd never make it in time!

rows.label: qst701506_msg0008
rows.name:
We'll have to perform first aid
ourselves.

rows.label: qst701506_msg0010
rows.name:
Ideally, something to soothe his throat.
We need to help him breathe easier.
